Title: Take a Promenade Along West Pier (2003)
Description: Since the partial collapse of part of one pier in Brighton, and the partial destruction by fire of another, I've been feeling the importance of preserving what yet remains of pier and promenade on Brighton Beach, one of the very best beaches in England. These photos are from a guided tour in 2003.

Title: The N Testament - re-interpreting the bible
Description: Between 5th April 1997 and 15th November 2000, I kept a page-a-day diary, but instead of writing, I (mostly) drew, and instead of a diary, I (ab)used a Good News Bible. It became The N Testament.
